  "text": "The starting point of the ADOP derivations is the expression for the vc-matrix of the real-valued parameters conditioned on the integer parameters, see Eq. (8). Using the determinant factorization rule, see e.g. [CITATION_1] , the determinant of this matrix can be written as:",
